# Default-ignore the existing workspace. This repository is used to distribute
# the OBE AI product workflow package and a minimal skill subset.
*

!.gitignore
!.codebuddy/
!.codebuddy/docs/
!.codebuddy/docs/ai-product-workflow-sharing/
!.codebuddy/docs/ai-product-workflow-sharing/**
!.codebuddy/skills/
!.codebuddy/skills/product/
!.codebuddy/skills/product/README.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/web3-cex-product-team.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/pipelines.yaml
!.codebuddy/skills/product/engineering-plan-review.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/web3-prd-figma-prompt.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/product-test-qa.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/web3-product-expert.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/doc-writer.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/market-researcher.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/data-analyst.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/cex-contract-testing-expert.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/ai-function-designer.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/OBE-product-ux-self-check.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/OBE-design-reference-playbook.md
!.codebuddy/skills/product/web3-product-experience-expert/
!.codebuddy/skills/product/web3-product-experience-expert/**
!scripts/
!scripts/sync-codebuddy-skills-to-cursor.sh
!scripts/sync-codebuddy-skills-to-codex.sh

.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
.env
.env.*
!.codebuddy/docs/ai-product-workflow-sharing/config/*.example
!.codebuddy/docs/ai-product-workflow-sharing/config/*.example.toml
